grep 'CENTOS' file.txt

grep 'centos' file.txt

grep -i 'Centos' file.txt

CENTOS Centos

sudo grep -ir 'Centos' /dir

returns all words without Centos - Invert Match Option

sudo grep -vir 'Centos' /dir

returns all exact words

grep -wi 'Centos' filename
grep -wir 'Centos' /dir

extract only matching option not lines

grep -io 'Centos' /filename
